0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(This manual defines the quarterly service routine for the fictional RTU-7 rooftop HVAC unit) Tj
0 -14 Td
(serving office and staging areas. It covers filter replacement, condensate inspection, belt) Tj
0 -14 Td
(condition, airflow verification, and restart documentation.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(The procedure is intended for trained maintenance technicians and shift leads. Production) Tj
0 -14 Td
(operators may assist with observation and restart confirmation, but they do not perform) Tj
0 -14 Td
(isolated service work unless the task card explicitly allows it.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(REQUIRED TOOLS AND PARTS) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Roof access permit, multimeter, differential pressure gauge, spare filters, belt tension) Tj
0 -14 Td
(tool, flashlight, and hand brush.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Approved replacement filters with the exact MERV rating listed on the asset card.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Portable radio or phone for contact with the building coordinator during shutdown and) Tj
0 -14 Td
(restart.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Weather-appropriate fall protection and non-slip footwear for roof access.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(HAZARDS AND CONTROLS) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Do not access the roof during lightning, freezing precipitation, or sustained high wind) Tj
0 -14 Td
(conditions.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Use the local disconnect to isolate the unit before opening service panels.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Take care around hot surfaces near compressor lines and sharp cabinet edges inside filter) Tj
0 -14 Td
(and blower compartments.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- If standing water is present near electrical sections, stop work and escalate before) Tj
0 -14 Td
(energizing the unit.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(PREPARATION) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Coordinate a service window with the building coordinator so occupants understand the) Tj
0 -14 Td
(temporary shutdown.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Isolate the RTU, verify fan stop, and inspect exterior panel condition, seals, and visible) Tj
0 -14 Td
(fasteners before opening the cabinet.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Remove used filters, compare size and rating to the asset card, and install matched) Tj
